verbose_text: Thus, the proliferation rate of myoblasts obtained by the stimulation of EGF alone in SKGM-2 medium can be enhanced by the stimulation of EGF combined with bFGF and HGF growth factors present in DFEFH medium.
evidence: proliferation rate of myoblasts obtained by the stimulation of EGF alone in SKGM-2 medium can be enhanced by the stimulation of EGF
